\/adam-created-image-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38414,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Adam: Allah created Adam in His image","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 20, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf one of you fights his brother, let him avoid the face. Verily, Allah created Adam in His image.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2612 Al-Nawawi said, \u201cA group of scholars said the \u2018image\u2019 is attributed to Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18807,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/04\/15\/tawbah-repent-seventy-times-day\/","url_meta":{"origin":38414,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tawbah: Repent to Allah seventy times a day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy Allah, I seek forgiveness from Allah and I repent to Him more than seventy times in a day.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6307 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousne